name: Monoploy
tagline: In the game MONOPOLY ELETRONIC BANK and similar the machine is to slow, so I've sold this problem with MONOPOLY
body:
# INSTRUCTIONS
## 1) Add all 4 users, but if you have less than 4 put a random name such as "none".
## 2) All users will have a turn, but if someone does not play a round, just put 0, as he did not won nor lost money.
## 3) To finish just answer yes or no for the question in the machine.
